</P>
<P>
The 23-member cabinet voted 21-2 to approve the agreement on
the implementation of the U.S.-brokered Wye accords, paving the
way for further Israeli withdrawals from the West Bank and the
launch of permanent peace talks with the Palestinians.
(BC-Israel-Palestinians-Deal)
</P>
