the local travel and tourism industry has worked hard over the
past few years to secure Hong Kong's position as the convention
and exhibition capital of Asia.
</P>
<P>
Pursuing its goal of becoming a travel and tourism industry hub,
the HKTA has won numerous bids to host travel industry meetings in
2000.
</P>
<P>
Apart from the Carlson conference, Hong Kong will receive
valuable exposure with the Pacific Asia Travel Association (PATA)
annual conference and conventions for the Meetings Industry
Association of Australia, Union des Foires Internationales,
International Congress &AMP; Convention Association and the Society of
Incentive Executives.
</P>
