<BODY>
<HEADLINE> May Says She May Retire </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
May, who was born in Britain but competes for Italy after
marrying an Italian, was convinced she was denied another world
championship gold when Spaniard Nuika Montalvo won with a disputed
jump on her last attempt in Seville.
</P>
<P>
Asked whether she would compete next season she said: "I have
one more competition and then I'll take a long holiday for maybe a
month.
</P>
<P>
"Tonight was encouraging and I'd say it's about 50 percent that
I'll carry on." 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
